{"tid":869972,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有錯嘅同學可以靠語言偽術以假亂真","createTime":"2018-10-20T16:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T18:20:36.000Z","uid":160932,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90604a7b0863e8e11b2cf29e53a9440167f51fb4","tid":869972,"uid":160932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"我中學被人背叛 我當眾屌7佢<br />\n係我公開係班試田屌7條粉皮 <br />\n跟住其他同學就同我say sorry <br />\n話原來誤會咗我<br />\n其他同學都識講 成件事<br />\n條粉皮失嘅係誠信<br />\n我唔啱嘅地方最多係唔應該當眾屌佢<br />\n條仆街最後係咁唱衰我<br />\n我同老師講 老師要我唔好再搞大件事<br />\n條粉皮日日唱衰我 堅持自己冇錯 <br />\n我本身就係邊緣人 冇乜朋友 亦都唔識語言偽術<br />\n同學都只不過係旁觀者 食花生 根本唔care事實嘅真相<br />\n利申：唔想再番學 好辛苦<br />\n（之前放錯台）"},{"pid":"8dfc2712dbfb61f79bc10147a62a306a07f3af7d","tid":869972,"uid":206727,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:44:45.000Z","msg":"一舊一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12341bff9204d7f1052cd6f26bc66d03f8816221","tid":869972,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:52:58.000Z","msg":"因為西哲說：事實勝於雄辯。我當初很以為然，現在才知道在我們中國，是不適用的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f84e7acac51d1730756894ec0ed769868f8829","tid":869972,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:54:42.000Z","msg":"黃奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6269da650077660dbf6c321eb23e9208d3062ddf","tid":869972,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n組織下先啦"},{"pid":"eb0b42d17073ecd81ed9b5df538662dd6785c04b","tid":869972,"uid":10165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"LF2?"},{"pid":"d2372c10d7a0267d113965f0e296e7ed59117609","tid":869972,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T18:20:36.000Z","msg":"唔知講